ation on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNAnnotationImage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationImage"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCluster":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCluster","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncluster","type":"topic","title":"MLNCluster","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNCluster","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A protocol that feature subclasses (i.e. those already conforming to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/docume